16 "§ 50-13.2B. Modification or enforcement of post-adoption contact agreement and order.
17 A former parent or adoptive parent who is party to a post-adoption contact agreement and
18 order entered pursuant to G.S. 7B-909.2 shall be governed by G.S. 7B-909.3."
